  <Docs>
    <summary>
      <span data-ttu-id="3c873-101">将包含句柄的托管对象包装到通过平台调用传递到非托管代码的资源中。</span>
      <span class="sxs-lookup">
        <span data-stu-id="3c873-101">Wraps a managed object holding a handle to a resource that is passed to unmanaged code using platform invoke.</span>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="3c873-102">从.NET Framework 2.0 的功能开始<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef>类已被取代<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle>类和派生的类，作为也由<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.CriticalHandle>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-102">Starting with the .NET Framework 2.0, the functionality of the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> class has been replaced by the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle> class and its derived classes, as well as by the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.CriticalHandle> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3c873-103">如果使用平台调用来调用的托管的对象和平台 invoke 调用之后，不在其他位置引用的对象，它可以为垃圾回收器以完成对托管的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-103">If you use platform invoke to call a managed object, and the object is not referenced elsewhere after the platform invoke call, it is possible for the garbage collector to finalize the managed object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3c873-104">此操作将释放资源并使该句柄，从而导致平台 invoke 调用失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-104">This action releases the resource and invalidates the handle, causing the platform invoke call to fail.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3c873-105">包装的句柄与<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef>保证的托管的对象不是垃圾回收之前的平台调用调用完成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-105">Wrapping a handle with <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> guarantees that the managed object is not garbage collected until the platform invoke call completes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3c873-106">有关平台的说明来调用服务，请参阅[使用非托管 DLL 函数](~/docs/framework/interop/consuming-unmanaged-dll-functions.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-106">For a description of platform invoke services, see [Consuming Unmanaged DLL Functions](~/docs/framework/interop/consuming-unmanaged-dll-functions.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3c873-107"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef>值类型，如<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.GCHandle>，是识别的互操作封送处理程序的特殊类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-107">The <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> value type, like <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.GCHandle>, is a special type recognized by the interop marshaler.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3c873-108">一个正常的、 nonpinned<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.GCHandle>还可以防止不及时垃圾回收，尚未<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef>提供更好的性能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-108">A normal, nonpinned <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.GCHandle> also prevents untimely garbage collection, yet <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> provides better performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3c873-109">尽管使用<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef>使对象保持活动状态的持续时间的平台 invoke 调用的是首选，还可以使用<xref:System.GC.KeepAlive%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>用于相同目的的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-109">Although using <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> to keep an object alive for the duration of a platform invoke call is preferred, you can also use the <xref:System.GC.KeepAlive%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method for the same purpose.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3c873-110"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef>构造函数采用两个参数：<xref:System.Object>表示包装和<xref:System.IntPtr>表示的非托管的句柄。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-110">The <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> constructor takes two parameters: an <xref:System.Object> representing the wrapper, and an <xref:System.IntPtr> representing the unmanaged handle.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3c873-111">互操作封送处理程序将仅将句柄传递给非托管代码，而可保证包装 (作为第一个参数传递给的构造函数`HandleRef`) 调用持续时间内保持活动状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3c873-111">The interop marshaler passes only the handle to unmanaged code, and guarantees that the wrapper (passed as the first parameter to the constructor of the `HandleRef`) remains alive for the duration of the call.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
